parameters: It seems to be locked from the other side.
There are documents related to Zaiborg. Would you like to read them?

By continuously feeding combatants to the Zaiborg, it has been
confirmed that they can grow to possess intelligence.

In terms of combat power, individuals have begun to emerge that far
surpass combatants, reaching the level of monster-class entities.

Lord Domudora's research is tremendous, but it's pointless if I end up
as mere fodder for the combatants.

In case of an emergency, I shall secure an escape route to the surface
without Lord Domudora's knowledge.
Hopefully, it won't come to a situation where it needs to be used...
